{"tid":912877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"組團去北森蒂納爾島，有咩要注意？","createTime":"2018-11-23T04:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T06:15:58.000Z","uid":4978,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5b924fa0fec0d65fe5b3fc892da75ef9a1037049","tid":912877,"uid":4978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:05:41.000Z","msg":"帶幾多個連登仔上去，先成到團？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/egvOTQO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FegvOTQO.png&h=f871ebff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n孟加拉灣一個小島上存在著一個極為神秘的部落，部落中的人可能一直過著原始且與世隔絕的生活。他們拒絕與外界接觸，只要有外人接近該島便有喪命的危險。這個島是位於孟加拉灣的北森蒂納爾島(North Sentinel Island)，面積與美國紐約曼哈頓島差不多大小。據估計，這個神秘部落已在該島上生活了6萬年。部落人被學者稱為森蒂納爾人(Sentinelese)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這個部落拒絕現代世界，並對外來人訴諸暴力。他們曾在2006年殺死2名在北森蒂納爾島附近捕魚的男子。報導稱，這個部落的人甚至向過往的飛機與直升機投擲石塊、射箭。截至目前，印度政府將試圖與森蒂納爾人接觸的行為視為犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n國際生存組織(Survival International)負責人史蒂芬-克裡(Stephen Corry)說，在英國19世紀殖民該群島時，印度安達曼群島上的大安達曼人部落因疾病蔓延而人口大幅減少。最近一個滅絕的是Bo部落，該部落最後一名成員4年前去世。安達曼當局為防止又有部落滅絕的唯一方法是，確保外人不去登上北森蒂納爾島。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20150424003852-260809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20150424003852-260809&d=GjAYn5dUZSke43U%2BKahIacP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=b763f189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20150424003852-260809</a>"},{"pid":"8e30f2240a69da75f4e281c31bb4d885557243a4","tid":912877,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:06:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔一個打幾個啦<br />\n洗驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a83ee16d1599165abcffe3d44695f28d5ddd27","tid":912877,"uid":163954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"近親繁殖，遲早都絕種"},{"pid":"ab209bedfd13ac01931a50e4be6a16ba3c0c767c","tid":912877,"uid":131522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f201ccc1d3a0ad1b1495a7db39445d92431ee826","tid":912877,"uid":57554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"張圖係亞馬遜入面啲Uncontacted Tribes 黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2289b1aa0884385872fb6bb0f346f932a8886ee1","tid":912877,"uid":470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f201ccc1d3a0ad1b1495a7db39445d92431ee826","tid":912877,"uid":57554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:14:35.000Z","msg":"張圖係亞馬遜入面啲Uncontacted Tribes 黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"台灣記者係咁求其"},{"pid":"0ebec6ec3d3e32ba69f0a233f4505556cf3a68b2","tid":912877,"uid":74003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"記得帶本聖經去"},{"pid":"c5a8b66752a3b12d41e4da8dd667398d33ca4240","tid":912877,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"上岸嗰陣真係要開槍辣低幾件先<br />\n不過而家文明社會唔會俾你咁做"},{"pid":"6303951b9414b57c414ac75446155e41e5a5e5b7","tid":912877,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T06:15:58.000Z","msg":"去羅湖差不多 又近 都係睇啲生番之嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}